title: University Of New England Armidale!
body: Looking for 3 players from UNE that are interested in this competition

replies.body:
Hey Damo, we up at the UNE Gaming Society are actually putting a team together for the comp. Add me on LoL and we will see what we can do.
We are planning on having a few teams if possible, an A team and a B team, (and if we have more people, a C team).
